title: Garmin China City Navigator V6.0 (Eng)
description:
Garmin China City Navigator V6.0 (Eng)

Due to China government policy the map has an offset off ca. 300-500m, that can be corrected by the original sofware delivered with the original Garmin device. there is no CD of this software on the market only delivered by SD-Card with the Garmin device.

Correction can be achieved by recalibrating each map (Mapedit).

By SOS
